Buddies is a focused rewrite of the RuneLite GIMP plugin's product shape.

The curated coordinate-to-place resolver in
src/main/java/com/buddies/location/LocationResolver.java is derived from the
local gim-plugin work under the BSD 2-Clause license included in LICENSE.

The group model, map rendering, ping overlay, notes, task manager, HTTP
fallback, and GIMP panel code were intentionally not copied.
